		<tr>
			<td class="BoardRowB" colspan=3>
				I have a general rant about the difficulty of having any trade skill as a dark race.  That is for another posting though.    <br> For now, I want to know, where can I get a spit.  I'm lvl 13 SK DEF.  I cannot find one anywhere in Neriak.   <br> I have started brewing, smithing, and tailoring, all of which are difficult for us Dark Elves, but Cooking will be especially hard if I cannot find a Spit.   <br> Should I just make an enchanter mule to get human illusion?  That seems like a really dumb way to do anything, and I am trying to avoid it.  Any suggestions will be helpful.		

