			<td class="BoardRowB" colspan=3>
				If your not KOS in Halas you can get a spit there.  Go across the lake and turn right at that fork right after you get out of the lake.  In one of the buildings there are 2 floors with a ramp leading up to the second floor with an NPC, forgot her name, standing in the middle of the ramp.  Continue past her and go to the first NPC you see after you go up the ramp, she sells spits.  You can also find baking supplies if you go down the hallway up there to the last npc in the hallway.  Hope this helps anyone else reading this thread. <br> Ginyu, Barbarian Warrior of The Tribunal <br> Tunare Server <br> 		

