			<td class="BoardRowB" colspan=3>
				Dark elves are very much KOS in Halas, as my enchantress found out when her illusion dropped at the wrong time.  :) <br>  <br> There are NO spits in any of the evil lands and precious little in the way of baking supplies other than Neriak (Oggok and Grobb are much worse on baking supplies). <br>  <br> Tislan in Traders Holiday (E. Freeport) is your best option as an evil race - my ogress had someone go buy her one, and in return paid for it, and also SoWed the kid's hunting party. <br>  <br> ~Niami DenMother <br> www.eqtraders.com		

